You're not

877
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:13,239
the only lawyer in this city.

878
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,400
Everyone else turned it down.

879
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,280
Why did it have to be you?

880
00:40:17,519 --> 00:40:19,199
[Can't you just try to understand me?]

881
00:40:19,559 --> 00:40:20,440
[You dare say]
[I don't understand you?]

882
00:40:21,119 --> 00:40:22,440
[After all these years?]

883
00:40:23,119 --> 00:40:24,559
[Have you thought about the kids?]

884
00:40:24,559 --> 00:40:25,800
[Have you thought about us?]

885
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,400
[You're being unreasonable.]

886
00:41:01,079 --> 00:41:02,599
[What if every memory of joy]

887
00:41:03,039 --> 00:41:04,679
[is swallowed by grief?]

888
00:41:06,079 --> 00:41:07,199
[I must search.]

889
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,480
[Even if the endless powdering of stars]

890
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:11,159
[in the Galaxy makes the quest seem hopeless,]

891
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,599
[and even if I must do it alone.]

892
00:41:14,079 --> 00:41:15,199
[This line from Galactic Empire]

893
00:41:15,199 --> 00:41:15,880
[is for you,]

894
00:41:16,119 --> 00:41:17,639
[a stranger who read the same comic as me.]

895
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,199
[Life]

896
00:41:19,519 --> 00:41:20,360
[can be bright]

897
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:21,440
[and carefree,]

898
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,039
[or it can drag you down]

899
00:41:23,039 --> 00:41:24,119
[and leave you lost.]

900
00:41:24,679 --> 00:41:25,719
[Should the bitterness consume you,]

901
00:41:26,199 --> 00:41:27,280
[keep seeking]

902
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:29,519
[and creating moments of joy.]

903
00:42:17,639 --> 00:42:18,159
Come on.

904
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:21,679
Xu Huaisong, you've got this.

905
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,119
You can do it.

906
00:42:57,400 --> 00:42:59,079
Don't touch it. You'll cut yourself.

907
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,159
It's fine.

908
00:43:03,159 --> 00:43:04,280
I'll clean it up later.

909
00:43:15,480 --> 00:43:16,079
Well,
Mr Xu, just leave it.

910
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:17,760
I'll take care of it.

911
00:43:18,199 --> 00:43:19,679
A cloth and some tape.

912
00:43:21,079 --> 00:43:21,559
Got it.

913
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:31,719
Mr Xu.

914
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,360
This type of bowl

915
00:43:59,679 --> 00:44:01,119
doesn't break into shards, right?

916
00:44:02,599 --> 00:44:03,360
What if it does?

917
00:44:23,559 --> 00:44:24,320
It's done.

918
00:44:25,679 --> 00:44:26,360
Mr Xu,

919
00:44:26,639 --> 00:44:28,440
go wash your hands and eat.

920
00:44:30,119 --> 00:44:30,559
Okay.

921
00:44:33,079 --> 00:44:34,360
Mr Xu, give it to me.

922
00:44:34,519 --> 00:44:36,079
No need. There are shards on it.

923
00:44:39,119 --> 00:44:39,719
That way.
